  <summary date="2026-04-06T13:05:56Z" status="Introduced in House">Diesel Emissions Reduction Act of 2025 

This bill reauthorizes through FY2029 a diesel emissions reduction program under which the Environmental Protection Agency provides grants, rebates, or loans for replacing diesel engines or retrofitting the engines with pollution control technologies.</summary>
